          <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0;">A computer-generated simulation of a three-dimensional environment that can be interacted with in a seemingly real way. Virtual reality is used in a variety of retail applications, such as product demos, training, and customer engagement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glossary-term" id="visual-merchandising" style="padding: 22px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <h3 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Visual Merchandising</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0;">The practice of developing floor plans and three-dimensional displays to maximize sales and provide an engaging shopping experience.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

