          <h3 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Wholesale</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0;">The selling of goods in large quantities to be retailed by others.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="letter-z" style="padding-top: 40px; padding-bottom: 80px;">
